President Muhammadu Buhari has again met with his Ghanaian counterpart, Nana Addo-Akufo, behind closed-door in Abuja on Thursday. Recall that Buhari and Asso-Akufo held a similar meeting on Feb. 22 at the Presidential Villa, Abuja. As at the time of filing this report, the agenda of the meeting has not been made public. Addo-Akufo is the current Chairman of ECOWAS.